== Trivia ==
*In ''RuneScape 3'', the [[rsw:Muspah|Muspah]] are a race of creatures created by the [[Gods|Elder God]] [[Mah]], as an amalgamation of the most fearsome creatures from her nightmares. In ''Old School RuneScape'', no other Muspah exist in the game, and little is known about the creatures' lore as of yet, but their origin story could likely be similar to their counterparts in ''RuneScape 3'', as evidenced by their examine text ({{mes|Imagination gone wild.}}) and the examine text of the [[Strange Creature]] ({{mes|A creature of nightmares.}}).
*The Muspah may have been named after {{WP|Muspelheim}}, the land of raging fire in Old Norse mythology.
*Physical similarities and a previous steel cannonball drop of 666 may be a reference to ''{{wp|Diablo II}}''{{'}}s demon Duriel.
*The "[[Scoreboard (Phantom Muspah)|scoreboard]]" plaque across from the entrance has Morse code that translates to "YOU GOT THIS BUDDY"

